title: 2009 Spanish National Badminton Championships
text: The 2009 Spanish National Badminton Championships was the 28th edition of the <a href="Spanish%20National%20Badminton%20Championships">Spanish National Badminton Championships</a>. It was held in <a href="Polideportivo%20Florida%20y%20Babel">Polideportivo Florida y Babel</a> located in <a href="Alicante">Alicante</a>, from May 8 to May 10, 2009.
